*   **[HVAC](/HVAC)** – Acronym for Heating, Ventilation, and Air Conditioning.

*   **[Hydraulics](/Hydraulics)** – The branch of [fluid mechanics](/Fluid_mechanics) concerned with the behavior of liquids under pressure.

*   **[Hydrostatics](/Hydrostatics)** – The branch of [fluid mechanics](/Fluid_mechanics) concerned with fluids at rest.

