### J

*   **[Jack chain](/Jack_chain)** – (Blank. Likely a specific type of chain used in lifting mechanisms.)

*   **[Jacking gear](/Jacking_gear)** – (Blank. Mechanical system for lifting or raising something.)

*   **[JIC fitting](/JIC_fitting)** – (Blank. Refers to fittings used in hydraulic systems, following Joint Industry Council standards.)

*   **[Joule](/Joule)** – The [SI](/SI) unit of [energy](/Energy), work, or heat. Named after [James Prescott Joule](/James_Prescott_Joule). It represents a specific amount of energy transfer.

