### M

*   **[Machine](/Machine)** – A device that uses [mechanical energy](/Mechanical_energy) to perform or assist in the performance of human tasks.

*   **[Machine learning](/Machine_learning)** – A subfield of [artificial intelligence](/Artificial_intelligence) that enables systems to learn from data without explicit programming.

