*   **[Microelectromechanical systems](/Microelectromechanical_systems)** – (MEMS) Devices that integrate mechanical and electrical components on a microscopic scale.

*   **[Micromachinery](/Micromachinery)** – (Blank. Refers to machinery operating at microscopic scales.)

