*   **[Microtechnology](/Microtechnology)** – Technology operating at microscopic scales.

*   **[Modulus of rigidity](/Modulus_of_rigidity)** – A measure of a material's resistance to [shear deformation](/Shear_stress). Also known as the shear modulus.

