*   **[Molecular nanotechnology](/Molecular_nanotechnology)** – (Blank. Nanotechnology involving the manipulation of individual molecules.)

*   **[Moment](/Moment_(physics))** – A measure of the effect of a [force](/Force) acting at a distance from a point or axis. Often referred to as [torque](/Torque).

*   **[Moment of inertia](/Moment_of_inertia)** – A measure of an object's resistance to changes in its [rotational](/Rotation) state of motion. It depends on mass and its distribution.

*   **[Motorcycle](/Motorcycle)** – A two-wheeled motor vehicle.

*   **[Multi-link suspension](/Multi-link_suspension)** – A complex [vehicle suspension](/Suspension_(vehicle)) system using multiple control arms to provide precise wheel control.

