### N

*   **[Nanotechnology](/Nanotechnology)** – The manipulation of matter on an atomic, molecular, and supramolecular scale.

*   **[Newton (unit)](/Newton_(unit))** – The [SI](/SI) unit of [force](/Force). Defined as the force required to accelerate a mass of 1 kilogram at a rate of 1 metre per second squared. Named after [Isaac Newton](/Isaac_Newton).

