### P

*   **[Pascal (unit)](/Pascal_(unit))** – The [SI](/SI) unit of [pressure](/Pressure), defined as one [newton](/Newton_(unit)) per square metre.

*   **[Physics](/Physics)** – The natural science that studies [matter](/Matter), its fundamental constituents, its [motion](/Motion_(physics)) and behavior through space and time, and the related entities of [energy](/Energy) and [force](/Force).

