*   **[Plasma processing](/Plasma_processing)** – (Blank. Uses plasma to modify material surfaces.)

*   **[Plasticity](/Plasticity_(physics))** – The ability of a material to undergo permanent [deformation](/Deformation_(engineering)) without fracturing.

*   **[Pneumatics](/Pneumatics)** – The branch of [fluid mechanics](/Fluid_mechanics) concerned with the behavior of gases under pressure.

*   **[Poisson's ratio](/Poisson%27s_ratio)** – The negative ratio of transverse strain to axial strain in the [elastic](/Elasticity_(physics)) deformation of a material.

*   **[Position vector](/Position_vector)** – A [vector](/Vector_(geometric)) that describes the position of a point relative to an origin.

*   **[Potential difference](/Potential_difference)** – See [Voltage](/Voltage).

*   **[Power](/Power_(physics))** – The rate at which [energy](/Energy) is transferred or converted. A [scalar](/Scalar_(physics)) quantity.

