*   **[Process control](/Process_control)** – The use of control systems to manage and regulate industrial processes.

*   **[Product lifecycle management](/Product_Lifecycle_Management)** – The process of managing the entire lifecycle of a product from inception, through engineering design and manufacture, to service and disposal.

