### Q

*   **[Quality](/Quality_(business))** – (Blank. Refers to the standard of something as measured against other things of a similar kind; the degree of excellence.)

*   **[Quality control](/Quality_control)** – A process by which a company checks the quality of its products or services.

*   **[Quality assurance](/Quality_assurance)** – A process-oriented way of preventing defects by making sure that established processes are being followed.

